text.1: At campaign rallies and in tweets, Trump falsely said the World Health Organization changed its position and “admitted that Donald Trump was right” about lockdowns. But the agency has said no such thing. https://t.co/9ttmhLwQRJ #FactCHAT
text.2: A Trump campaign ad uses an out-of-context video clip to claim Biden admitted he will come for the guns of Americans if he’s elected. In the unedited video, Biden was talking about his opposition to so-called “assault weapons” — not all firearms. https://t.co/0L1MrNW2hn #FactCHAT
text.3: Trump has complained on a few recent occasions that -- for partisan reasons -- people have shifted from saying COVID-19 immunity was lifelong to now saying it lasts only a few months. But experts haven’t changed their estimates for immunity. https://t.co/L5sPw0mqTF #FactCHAT
